Pool 
Game genre : casual
Gameplay: player use cue ball to hit the ball with different color(represent missing artefact), collect the correct artefact ball
Rules: The ball change color when hit cushion
	2 balls of same color vanish when hit each other, which is called collect
	If you collect a pair of balls with right color, you get 1 soul.
	Cue ball hit the ball and turns it to the next color.
	Color order: red->yellow->blue(only 3)
	Collect 3 souls to win.
#just a random casual game for visitors who like to play games for now
